{"tid":1439484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說罷買，要說長期儲錢","createTime":"2019-08-10T06:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T08:22:15.000Z","uid":33939,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6af1d7de52aaebcad8e626d8478e8f191fb2f98a","tid":1439484,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"短期罷買，你只係將想買嘅嘢延遲幾日買，而且購買意慾係人都有。<br />\n<br />\n反而儲錢，盡量減少消費。或盡量幫襯良心小店，甚至小店可以搞多啲優惠，咁就可以互專互利，亦可以解決到消費嘅慾望。<br />\n<br />\n而且慳到嚟嘅錢，又可以拎去支持下義士，或者立場新聞咁樣。自私啲咪攞嚟去下旅行，支持下中共所謂嘅外國勢力囉。"},{"pid":"de35b271e9956a7ee2a0cc51348cad95b12c640f","tid":1439484,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:23:42.000Z","msg":"得得得"},{"pid":"1180bd3914b93fc1bd7657b8d9b5163e43708030","tid":1439484,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ef3b3618faf43cd523be8020f26940acd907cd7b","tid":1439484,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"df47f00031bc15d93a3c4ce54d3c52fb7164c7e4","tid":1439484,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:22:15.000Z","msg":"得"}]}